Requirements-
1. JAVA 
Installing java-

step 1 download-
https://java.com/download

step2 after download install from setup-

step3- set environment variable-

setx /M JAVA_HOME "path to jdk installed"

example-
setx /M JAVA_HOME "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_17"

2.Python2.7 

install python 2.7 from-
 
https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-2713/

adding python to path-

setx path "%path%";"path to python27.exe"

adding java to path-


setx path "%path%";"path to jdk as above"

